{
  "stem": "22944.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was so excited, like getting a real gift, to be with another child, that all I was saying to her that, when the liberation will come, I'm going to race you.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I will walk and run that you will never catch me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But-- and that was something so terribly important for me, to be able to walk and to be out in nature and to be able to see fresh air and birds and flowers and trees.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when actually, physically this happened, the war was over, and Duli said, well, now you have to go race me, a few days after the liberation.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, of course, my leg was so swollen, because the circulation stopped-- we didn't do any movement-- that I hardly can walk for about a month.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This was a very important incident for me to remind you that things like that were happening.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, we-- right a few days after, went back to our old house in Podzamska, August the 29th or 28th-- went to look for our [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] belonging, and of course, finding out what's happened to our father.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is still in Nitra.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is still in Nitra.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we went back out of this-- when we become slightly quieter, after about a week or two, when we really felt we could get out.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very, very dangerous to go out because practically every woman, young and old, was raped, in the whole town.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nine months afterwards, it was an incredible city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nearly everybody was pregnant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went back to that-- to our apartment, just to see that the building was bombed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, strangely enough, it was not looted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was bombed.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
